Module it.polimi.ingsw
Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.handler.util

Interface TriPredicate<T,​U,​R>

Type Parameters:
T - the type of the first argument to the predicate
U - the type of the second argument to the predicate
R - the type of the third argument to the predicate
Functional Interface:
This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
@FunctionalInterface
public interface TriPredicate<T,​U,​R>
Represents a predicate (boolean-valued function) of three arguments. This is the three-arity specialization of Predicate.
